<bibRefCitation id="EFBC4B03FFF4636330258A3FFE16F2AC" author="Speight, M. C. D. &amp; Sarthou, J. - P." box="[568,859,1397,1424]" pageId="3" pageNumber="128" pagination="1 - 139" refId="ref5733" refString="Speight, M. C. D. &amp; Sarthou, J. - P. 2017. StN keys for the identiFIcation of the European species of various genera of Syrphidae 2017. Syrph the Net, the database of European Syrphidae (Diptera), 99, 1 - 139. Syrph the Net publications, Dublin." type="journal article" year="2017">Speight &amp; Sarthou, 2017</bibRefCitation>
